    <title id="1">The Admin Menu</title>
    <shortdesc id="2"> The <uicontrol id="3">Admin</uicontrol> menu contains
        selections for managing tenants (projects), tenant resources, and users. It is available
        when <uicontrol id="4">admin</uicontrol> is selected as the <nameliteral id="170">Current
            Tenant</nameliteral>.</shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <author id="5">Jim Owens</author>
        <author id="144">Pedro Sanchez</author>
    </prolog>
    <refbody>
        <section id="section_N10027_N10024_N10001" id="6">
